{"tid":1201062,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"我想問撐反送中 但事不關己咁 係等緊啲乜？","createTime":"2019-06-11T02:18:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-11T02:54:45.000Z","uid":207000,"like":8,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"46828a2079caa2a76f2b012a9e8d18ef298ecf86","tid":1201062,"uid":207000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T02:18:41.000Z","msg":"係咪諗住條法例通過唔到 就係到慶祝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？<br />\n但自己就乜都唔做 等睇戲？<br />\n你老母養大你咁多年 都剩係識得隔岸觀火<br />\n表面上撐撚哂咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n結果呢. 做咗啲乜 剩係打開手機睇直播 <br />\n<br />\n睇到個心都酸 跟住冷靜完就訓教？<br />\n我睇到好多人story仲可以吃喝玩樂<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唔係問題呀.你政治冷感</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">最撚大問題係你啲旅行story食野story<br />\n中間夾住個白色洋紫荊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span><br />\n係到搏乜春</span><br />\n每日簽到？提升身份認同？<br />\n<br />\n好心關自己事嘅 唔出都諗下點幫啦<br />\n咁多人教唔出仲可以點幫 睇下啦<br />\n唔好得把口 <br />\n講埋啲乜柒<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">呀～我唔知點幫<br />\n我唔識幫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span><br />\n我一拳打撚到你飛天<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nDLLM剩係識得po 我老母都識啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SECZfsT.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSECZfsT.png&h=cabce683&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n保護自己，唔好再手無寸鐵。<br />\n反正掂一下都叫襲警.<br />\n咁仲等咩 香港都上咗<span style=\"color: red;\">斷頭台</span>。<br />\n<br />\n唔知仲講得幾多次..<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\">我係一個香港人</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\">NOT FROM CHINA</span></span>"},{"pid